'''Renée Fleming''' (born [[February 14]], [[1959]]) is an American soprano opera singer.<ref>{{webcite|author=The Editors of Encyclopaedia Britannica|articleurl=http://www.britannica.com/biography/Renee-Fleming|articlename=Renée Fleming, American Singer|dated=|website=[http://www.britannica.com Encyclopedia Britannica]|accessed=}}</ref>

She has performed vocals for a number of movies, notably [[The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King]]. She carried out vocals on four tracks of the soundtrack ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King - The Complete Recordings]]'': "[[The Grace of Undómiel]]", "[[Mount Doom (soundtrack)|Mount Doom]]", "[[The Eagles]]", and "[[The Fellowship Reunited]]".
